# Personal Project Overrides (CLAUDE.local.md)
#
# Copy this file to CLAUDE.local.md and customize for your local setup.
# CLAUDE.local.md is gitignored and won't be shared with the team.
#
# Rename: cp CLAUDE.local.md.example CLAUDE.local.md

## My preferences

# - I prefer verbose test output: use `uv run pytest -v` instead of `-q`
# - Always show full tracebacks: use `--tb=long`
# - My local API runs on port 9000, not 8000

## My environment

# - Local database URL: postgresql://localhost:5432/mydb
# - My sandbox API base URL: https://dev.example.com
# - I use tmux, so notify-send doesn't work — disable notification hooks

## My workflow

# - I like to see git diffs before committing
# - Don't auto-format on save — I do it manually
# - When reviewing PRs, also check for accessibility issues
